#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.ravel.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.ravel"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.misc.ravel.ravel:1 of
msgid "Return a contiguous flattened tensor."
msgstr "返回一个连续的扁平化张量。"

#: maxframe.tensor.misc.ravel.ravel:3 of
msgid ""
"A 1-D tensor, containing the elements of the input, is returned.  A copy "
"is made only if needed."
msgstr "返回一个包含输入元素的1维张量。仅在需要时才会进行复制。"

#: maxframe.tensor.misc.ravel.ravel of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.misc.ravel.ravel:6 of
msgid "Input tensor.  The elements in `a` are packed as a 1-D tensor."
msgstr "输入张量。`a` 中的元素被打包成一个1维张量。"

#: maxframe.tensor.misc.ravel.ravel:8 of
msgid ""
"The elements of `a` are read using this index order. 'C' means to index "
"the elements in row-major, C-style order, with the last axis index "
"changing fastest, back to the first axis index changing slowest.  'F' "
"means to index the elements in column-major, Fortran-style order, with "
"the first index changing fastest, and the last index changing slowest. "
"Note that the 'C' and 'F' options take no account of the memory layout of"
" the underlying array, and only refer to the order of axis indexing.  'A'"
" means to read the elements in Fortran-like index order if `a` is Fortran"
" *contiguous* in memory, C-like order otherwise.  'K' means to read the "
"elements in the order they occur in memory, except for reversing the data"
" when strides are negative.  By default, 'C' index order is used."
msgstr ""
"使用此索引顺序读取 `a` 中的元素。'C' 表示按行主序（C 风格）索引元素，最后"
"一个轴索引变化最快，第一个轴索引变化最慢。'F' 表示按列主序（Fortran 风格"
"）索引元素，第一个索引变化最快，最后一个索引变化最慢。注意，'C' 和 'F' "
"选项不考虑底层数组的内存布局，仅涉及轴索引的顺序。'A' 表示如果 `a` 在内存"
"中是 Fortran *连续* 的，则以类似 Fortran 的索引顺序读取元素，否则按 C "
"风格顺序读取。'K' 表示按照元素在内存中出现的顺序读取，但在步长为负时会"
"反转数据。默认使用 'C' 索引顺序。"

#: maxframe.tensor.misc.ravel.ravel of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.misc.ravel.ravel:24 of
msgid ""
"**y** -- If `a` is a matrix, y is a 1-D tensor, otherwise y is a tensor "
"of the same subtype as `a`. The shape of the returned array is "
"``(a.size,)``. Matrices are special cased for backward compatibility."
msgstr ""
"**y** -- 如果 `a` 是矩阵，则 y 是一个1维张量；否则 y 是与 `a` 相同子类型"
"的张量。返回数组的形状为 ``(a.size,)``。矩阵为向后兼容而做了特殊处理。"

#: maxframe.tensor.misc.ravel.ravel of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.misc.ravel.ravel:32 of
msgid ":py:obj:`Tensor.flat`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.misc.ravel.ravel:33 of
msgid "1-D iterator over an array."
msgstr "数组上的1维迭代器。"

#: maxframe.tensor.misc.ravel.ravel:35 of
msgid ":py:obj:`Tensor.flatten`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.misc.ravel.ravel:36 of
msgid "1-D array copy of the elements of an array in row-major order."
msgstr "按行主序排列的数组元素的1维数组副本。"

#: maxframe.tensor.misc.ravel.ravel:38 of
msgid ":py:obj:`Tensor.reshape`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.misc.ravel.ravel:39 of
msgid "Change the shape of an array without changing its data."
msgstr "在不改变数据的情况下改变数组的形状。"

#: maxframe.tensor.misc.ravel.ravel:42 of
msgid "示例"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.misc.ravel.ravel:43 of
msgid "It is equivalent to ``reshape(-1)``."
msgstr "它等价于 ``reshape(-1)``。"

